<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, August 21 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange closed at 1,718.06 points on Saturday, down
5.94 points from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 1,051,430 shares changed hands in 934 deals and the
turnover was 3.96 billion rials (about 1.32 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
During the trading session, shares of 26 companies made
gains while those of 23 others declined. 
</P>
