<HEADLINE> Yeltsin to Visit Bishkek Next Week </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, August 21 (Xinhua) -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin
will fly to Bishkek, Kirghizia, Tuesday to attend the summit of
the so-called "Shanghai Five" -- China, Kazakhstan, Kirghizia,
