Locatelli, who started from pole position, was so upset after
being overtaken by Melandri on the final lap that he lost control
and crashed out with no one chasing.
</P>
<P>
Championship leader Masao Azuma of Japan finished 12th on his
Honda, but still held a four-point lead over Spanish Emilio
Alzamora with six events remaining. 
