<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 22 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 15 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
August 23, issued by China's Central Meteorological Station this
evening:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 20 degrees C., max. 29 degrees C., cloudy to
thunder showers, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shenyang: min. 17 degrees C., max. 28 degrees C., clear, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin: min. 20 degrees C., max. 29 degrees C., thunder
showers, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Xi'an: min. 22 degrees C., max. 33 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
