<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 22 (Xinhua) -- Highlights of today's major
Beijing-based newspapers:
</P>
<P>
 People's Daily
</P>
<P>
-- The paper carries an editorial to expound the significance
of the 22nd Universal Postal Union Congress scheduled to open on
Monday, saying that it will be a window for China to exhibit its
