<HEADLINE> Croatia Beats Malta 2-1 in Euro 2000 Qualifier </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ZAGREB, August 21 (Xinhua) -- World Cup semifinalists Croatia
fought out a hard 2-1 victory over minnows Malta in a Euro 2000
qualifier Group Eight match here on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Zvonimir Soldo secured the win for the host side with a well-
taken 55th minute header after Mario Stanic opened the accounting
in the first half.
</P>
<P>
